 \left\{ \begin{array}{rcrcrcl} \alpha x_1&+&&&\alpha^2x_3&=&1,\\ x_1&+&x_2&+&\alpha x_3&=&0,\\ (1+\alpha)x_1&+&\alpha x_2&&&=&\alpha. \end{array}\right. 
 A=\left(\begin{array}{ccc} \alpha&0&\alpha^2\\ 1&1&\alpha\\ 1+\alpha&\alpha&0 \end{array}\right). 
 \det A=\alpha^3+\alpha^3+\alpha^2(\alpha+1)=0+\alpha^3+\alpha^2=1+\alpha+\alpha^2\neq0, 
 \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1&1&\alpha&0\\ \alpha&0&\alpha^2&1\\ 1+\alpha&\alpha&0&\alpha \end{array}\right). 
 \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1&1&\alpha&0\\ 0&\alpha&\alpha^2+\alpha^2&1\\ 0&\alpha+(1+\alpha)&\alpha(1+\alpha)&\alpha \end{array}\right) =\left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1&1&\alpha&0\\ 0&\alpha&0&1\\ 0&1&\alpha+\alpha^2&\alpha \end{array}\right). 
 \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1&1&\alpha&0\\ 0&1&0&1+\alpha^2\\ 0&1&\alpha+\alpha^2&\alpha \end{array}\right). 
 \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1&1+1&\alpha&1+\alpha^2\\ 0&1&0&1+\alpha^2\\ 0&1+1&\alpha+\alpha^2&\alpha+(1+\alpha^2) \end{array}\right)= \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1&0&\alpha&1+\alpha^2\\ 0&1&0&1+\alpha^2\\ 0&0&\alpha+\alpha^2&1+\alpha+\alpha^2 \end{array}\right). 
 (1+\alpha)(1+\alpha+\alpha^2)=\alpha^3\cdot\alpha^5=\alpha^8=\alpha\cdot\alpha^7=\alpha, 
 \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1&0&\alpha&1+\alpha^2\\ 0&1&0&1+\alpha^2\\ 0&0&1&\alpha \end{array}\right). 
 \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1&0&0&1+\alpha^2+\alpha^2\\ 0&1&0&1+\alpha^2\\ 0&0&1&\alpha \end{array}\right)= \left(\begin{array}{cccc} 1&0&0&1\\ 0&1&0&1+\alpha^2\\ 0&0&1&\alpha \end{array}\right). 
 x_1=1,\quad x_2=1+\alpha^2,\quad x_3=\alpha.
